# User <kbd>Model</kbd>

> Represents a registered user.

**Category:** Identity · **Since:** 1.0 · **Defined in:** \`../../../../../tmp/zenstack-schema-2a11e8ef-9d2f-4f9e-acd9-5bdefab2c27d.zmodel\`

